platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: On desktop, Affinity Publisher won our Mac App of the Year Award, providing all the tools necessary to lay out a large-format photo book, a poster for a school play, or a brochure for your small business. The new Affinity Publisher 2 lets you do all this and more using an interface optimized for touchscreen.

On desktop, this won our Mac App of the Year Award, providing tools to lay out anything from posters and brochures to books and magazines. The iPad version lets you do all this and more with an interface optimised for touchscreen.
